1. *Častiš* me? (Are you treating me?)
2. Nadam se da ćeš me *častiti* pićem večeras. (I hope you will treat me to a drink tonight.)
3. On je uvek spreman da *časti* druge. (He is always ready to treat others.)
4. *Častio* je svoje prijatelje večerom. (He treated his friends to dinner.)
5. Njegova velikodušnost je u tome što uvek *časti* druge. (His generosity lies in always treating others.)
6. Sviđa mi se tvoja nova haljina, *častim* te kafom. (I like your new dress, let me treat you to coffee.)
7. Kao *častan* čovek, uvek drži svoju reč. (As an honorable man, he always keeps his word.)
8. Ona je *častna* osoba koja uvek radi na principima. (She is an honorable person who always works on principles.)
9. *Čast* mi je što sam dobio ovu nagradu. (It is an honor for me to have received this award.)
10. On je dao svoj život u *čast* domovine. (He gave his life in honor of his homeland.)